d798d270cacbf7ff9f5be420818\" data-recommend-id=\"image://3bd6cd798d270cacbf7ff9f5be420818\" data-format=\"png\" data-width=\"2559\" data-height=\"1440\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"The Switch 2 Joy-Cons are shown being removed from the device.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt=\"The Switch 2 Joy-Cons are shown being removed from the device.\" data-link-reference=\"\" data-link-target=\"\" data-syndicationrights=\"true\" data-imagerights=\"fair-use\" data-hide=\"false\" data-hidecredit=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(max-width: 49.94em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_965/3bd6cd798d270cacbf7ff9f5be420818.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 50em) and (max-width: 63.69em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1315/3bd6cd798d270cacbf7ff9f5be420818.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 63.75em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1600/3bd6cd798d270cacbf7ff9f5be420818.jpg\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"The Switch 2 Joy-Cons are shown being removed from the device.\" data-chomp-id=\"3bd6cd798d270cacbf7ff9f5be420818\" data-format=\"png\" data-height=\"1440\" data-alt=\"The Switch 2 Joy-Cons are shown being removed from the device.\" data-anim-src=\"\" src=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_645/3bd6cd798d270cacbf7ff9f5be420818.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003eScreenshot: Nintendo / Kotaku\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cspan data-id=\"3bd6cd798d270cacbf7ff9f5be420818\" data-recommend-id=\"image://3bd6cd798d270cacbf7ff9f5be420818\" data-format=\"png\" data-width=\"2559\" data-height=\"1440\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"The Switch 2 Joy-Cons are shown being removed from the device.\" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eIf you missed it, Nintendo finally \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/switch-2-reveal-trailer-date-nintendo-mario-kart-9-1851739487\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/switch-2-reveal-trailer-date-nintendo-mario-kart-9-1851739487\"\u003eunveiled the Switch 2\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e this morning. It looks pretty much exactly like \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/switch-2-dock-joy-cons-rumors-leaks-ces-2025-1851735925\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/switch-2-dock-joy-cons-rumors-leaks-ces-2025-1851735925\"\u003ewhat the leaks said it would\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e. It’s a bigger, presumably more powerful version of the beloved console/handheld hybrid that has magnetic Joy-Cons and can play your old Switch games, too. That \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/switch-2-joy-con-nintendo-new-features-1851735307\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/switch-2-joy-con-nintendo-new-features-1851735307\"\u003emight not sound that exciting to some\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e, but it’s nice to finally have Nintendo talking about the thing instead of having to scrape the bottom of a leaking barrel for crumbs of information. We’ll get a longer presentation on the device through a Nintendo Direct \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/nintendo-direct-switch-2-release-date-april-2025-1851740848\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/nintendo-direct-switch-2-release-date-april-2025-1851740848\"\u003eon April 2\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e, as well as some opportunities to play the thing \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/nintendo-switch-2-experience-early-play-la-nyc-dallas-1851740842\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/nintendo-switch-2-experience-early-play-la-nyc-dallas-1851740842\"\u003ein select cities\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e in the days and weeks that follow. But how is the internet reacting to this first tease? There’s enough excitement, disappointment, and bewilderment to go around. - Kenneth Shepard \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/nintendo-switch-2-trailer-internet-reaction-jokes-memes-1851741135\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/nintendo-switch-2-trailer-internet-reaction-jokes-memes-1851741135\"\u003eRead More\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure id=\"\" data-id=\"e7b234e23a4577bbfcbdb8522d18d6ca\" data-recommend-id=\"image://e7b234e23a4577bbfcbdb8522d18d6ca\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"An image shows Weird Al holding two Switch 2 consoles. \" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt=\"An image shows Weird Al holding two Switch 2 consoles. \" data-link-reference=\"\" data-link-target=\"\" data-syndicationrights=\"true\" data-imagerights=\"getty\" data-hide=\"false\" data-hidecredit=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(max-width: 49.94em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_965/e7b234e23a4577bbfcbdb8522d18d6ca.jpg\"/\u003e\