at’s more powerful, sleeker, and supports all the old games. However, is this new console too...safe? Boring? This is what \u003cem\u003eKotaku’s \u003c/em\u003estaff debated shortly after the reveal, and here’s our lightly edited debate straight from Slack. - Zack Zwiezen \u003cspan\u003e\u003ca data-ga=\"[[\u0026#34;Embedded Url\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;Internal link\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;https://kotaku.com/switch-2-nintendo-debate-weird-enough-normal-kotaku-1851741231\u0026#34;,{\u0026#34;metric25\u0026#34;:1}]]\" href=\"https://kotaku.com/switch-2-nintendo-debate-weird-enough-normal-kotaku-1851741231\"\u003eRead More\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cfigure id=\"\" data-id=\"f866786c5c4235f2021a21bafc005910\" data-recommend-id=\"image://f866786c5c4235f2021a21bafc005910\" data-format=\"jpg\" data-width=\"1920\" data-height=\"1080\" data-lightbox=\"false\" data-alt=\"An image shows The Punisher as seen in Rivals. \" data-recommended=\"false\" data-hide=\"false\" contenteditable=\"false\" draggable=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv contenteditable=\"false\" data-alt=\"An image shows The Punisher as seen in Rivals. \" data-link-reference=\"\" data-link-target=\"\" data-syndicationrights=\"true\" data-imagerights=\"fair-use\" data-hide=\"false\" data-hidecredit=\"false\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource media=\"(max-width: 49.94em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_965/f866786c5c4235f2021a21bafc005910.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 50em) and (max-width: 63.69em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1315/f866786c5c4235f2021a21bafc005910.jpg\"/\u003e\u003csource media=\"(min-width: 63.75em)\" type=\"image/jpeg\" srcset=\"https://i.kinja-img.com/image/upload/c_fit,q_60,w_1600/f866786c5c4235f2021a21bafc005910.jpg\"/\u003e\u003cimg alt=\"An image shows The Punisher as seen in Rivals. \" data-chomp-id=\"f866786c5c4235f20